data.description: Amazing views from this great permanent home or vacation getaway This home has so many recent upgrades to offer, to include new hi-efficiency hvac, toilet, dishwasher and stove, that includes built in air-fryer. New wood stove in living room.  All new light fixtures throughout the house, and new tiling in the bathrooms. New wood flooring in the kitchen. The amazing views can be seen from the front two bedrooms and living room. Newly finished room downstairs could be used for multiple uses. Rough in, in unfished basement to allow for possible 3rd bathroom. Sellers offering their assumable VA 2.5% loan to qualified VA buyers. High Knob offers a community center, swimming pool, tennis court and much more. Just minutes to I66, the river, vineyards, shopping, hospitals, hiking (High Knob has its own access to the Appalachian Trail) and downtown Front Royal. High Knob also has its own public water system and snow crew. The "HOA" fees are listed as a special tax in the tax record and are part of the real estate taxes.
